        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Want blog + GBP + social shipped on one plan?</h4>
            <p>Get a <strong>free 24-hour demo</strong>. We'll publish a real blog post, a GBP update, and a social post to your accounts so you can review the multi-format output before you commit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">Book my free demo <span>&rarr;</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">24-hour delivery · No card</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="what-is">What is an AI content creation tool?</h2>
        <p>An AI content creation tool generates marketing content from prompts, briefs, or product data. The category covers four broad types:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Multi-format generators</strong> — Jasper, Copy.ai, Writesonic. Blog + social + email + ad copy in one app.</li>
          <li><strong>Visual creators</strong> — Canva Magic Studio. Image + design + brand templates.</li>
          <li><strong>Video creators</strong> — Synthesia. AI avatars and video scripts.</li>
          <li><strong>Done-for-you publishers</strong> — theStacc. Topic plan, drafting, image, schema, publish across blog + GBP + social.</li>
        </ul>

