          <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">10</div><div class="stat-lbl">Tools Tested</div><div class="stat-delta">$15 → $167/mo plans</div></div>
          <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">5</div><div class="stat-lbl">Formats Tested</div><div class="stat-delta">Blog · social · video · image · ad copy</div></div>
          <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">4</div><div class="stat-lbl">Scoring Criteria</div><div class="stat-delta">Quality · coverage · publish · price</div></div>
        </div>

        <p>We scored output quality without editing, format coverage breadth, native publishing integrations to live channels, and total monthly cost including image and credit add-ons.</p>

